   ```

5. Browser Compatibility Testing:
   - Test optimizations in all supported browsers:
     - Chrome, Firefox, Safari, Edge
     - Mobile browsers
   - Verify performance improvements are consistent across browsers
   - Check for any browser-specific issues with the new event handling system

6. Load Testing:
   - Simulate high DOM operation frequency:
   ```javascript
   function loadTest() {
     // Create a complex character form
     const form = createComplexCharacterForm();

     // Simulate rapid user interactions
